betterquesting:10.name:8: You Have Too Many Servers, What Server is What?
betterquesting:10.desc:8:
StoneLegion is a community that mostly runs Minecraft Game Servers, but we do run other game servers as well from time to time.

This is what we offer for the GTNH community.

[warn]GTNH 2025 (This Server):[/warn]
- Server Launched near the end of 2024
- Public Server, No Whitelist
- No Wipe and continued support as long there are players.
- Long Term Support & Continued Updates
- IP: mc.stonelegion.com:25565

[warn]GTNH 2026[/warn]
- Server Launched near the end of 2025
- Public Server, No Whitelist
- No Wipe and continued support as long there are players.
- Long Term Support & Continued Updates
- IP: mc.stonelegion.com:25575

[warn]GTNH: 2021:[/warn] 
- Server Launched sometime in 2021
- Private Server now, to join you would need to donate at least $20 USD Directly for entry. (This is to protect the current community / progress)
- No Wipe and continued support as long there are players.
- Long Term Support & Continued Updates
- IP: mc.stonelegion.com:2021
